				'It is realised with the suppliers, the subcontractors and the service providers of the aeronautical and spatial sector, implanted in the large  Southwest of France.\n\nThis survey allows to know better the tissue of establishments connected to the contractors of the aircraft and spatial manufacturing. It also allows a better knowledge of the regional economic climate, very close to the activity of the sector.',
