				"Enquête sur les consommations d'énergie et les investissements antipollution dans les petits établissements de moins de 20 salariés",
			abstractLg2:
				'The objective of the survey is to estimate the energy purchases and the antipollution expenses made by industrial establishments with fewer than 20 employees. The survey will enable to complete, for units with less than 20 employees, the data provided by the surveys EACEI and Antipol in order to meet across the whole field with EU regulations and to establish the accounts of the environment.\nTwo European regulations are at the origin of the survey:\nThe European regulation concerning business structural statistics (EC No. 251/2009), which asks to provide environmental protection expenditure by environmental domain, activity and by company size. \nThe regulation No. 844/2010 concerning energy statistics, which requires data on the quantities consumed.',
