				'The purpose of the survey is to measure the difficulties met by Small and Medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) employing at least 10 persons to get finance and in the means and sources of financing looked for in 2007, in 2010 and over the period 2011-2013.\nAn other scope is to study the high-growth enterprises and "gazelles" (high-growth enterprises that are up to 5 years old), in particular as comparison with the United States.',
